data.description: Welcome to this charming 5 bedroom, 3 full bath craftsman style home, with rear entry garage. Enjoy walking trails, a dog park, a playground, pool and exercise facility within your neighborhood. Step inside and be greeted by an inviting floor plan seamlessly connecting the gourmet kitchen with spacious living area. The main floor boasts spacious rooms, a fireplace, hardwood floors, coffered ceilings in the dining room, a bedroom, and a full bath. Upstairs, the owners suite offers a private retreat with a luxurious ensuite. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms are upstairs with a third full bathroom and loft. The fenced backyard is ideal for outdoor gatherings. In close proximity to the coming Lions Gate Studio, Sweetwater Creek, Atlanta, I-20, easy access to ATL airport. HOA includes cable, internet, and access to all the community has to offer! Cable and WI-FI is included in monthly HOA.  Welcome home!!
